Subject: E-mail alerts not working
Description: Need help figuring out why e-mail alerts are no longer working. We've had this issue in the past.
Solution_Comment__c:
alerts cache was rebuilt
We checked and the test emails were coming into your mailbox.

We did the following:
- cleared the alert cache on the EPP server
- cleared /var/spool
- restarted the services
- checked database for alerts(no pending alerts)
- checked EPP Alert configuration
